ivardefs.name: concentration
ivardefs.desc: The strength per unitary volume (or mass).

ivardefs.name: concentrationLowLimit
ivardefs.desc: A lower limit for the strength per unitary volume (or mass), for when there is a range. The concentration attribute then becomes the upper limit.

ivardefs.name: country_
ivardefs.desc: The country or countries for which the strength range applies.

ivardefs.name: measurementPoint
ivardefs.desc: For when strength is measured at a particular point or distance.

ivardefs.name: presentation
ivardefs.desc: The quantity of substance in the unit of presentation, or in the volume (or mass) of the single pharmaceutical product or manufactured item.

ivardefs.name: presentationLowLimit
ivardefs.desc: A lower limit for the quantity of substance in the unit of presentation. For use when there is a range of strengths, this is the lower limit, with the presentation attribute becoming the upper limit.

ivardefs.name: referenceStrength_
ivardefs.desc: Strength expressed in terms of a reference substance.

properties.desc: Quantity of the substance or specified substance present in the manufactured item or pharmaceutical product.
